#: includes/Admin.php:400
msgid ""
"The B2Brouter plugin allows you to automatically generate and send "
"electronic invoices for your WooCommerce orders."
msgstr ""
"Le plugin B2Brouter vous permet de générer et d'envoyer automatiquement des "
"factures électroniques pour vos commandes WooCommerce."

#: includes/Admin.php:410
msgid "Next Steps"
msgstr "Étapes suivantes"

#: includes/Admin.php:411
msgid "Step 1 — Get your B2Brouter credentials"
msgstr "Étape 1 — Obtenez vos identifiants B2Brouter"

#: includes/Admin.php:413
msgid "Register at app.b2brouter.net"
msgstr "S'inscrire sur app.b2brouter.net"

#: includes/Admin.php:414
msgid "Purchase an eDocExchange subscription."
msgstr "Souscrivez un abonnement eDocExchange."

#: includes/Admin.php:414
msgid "First month is for free!"
msgstr "Le premier mois est gratuit !"

#: includes/Admin.php:415
msgid "Go to Developers → API Keys in your B2Brouter dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Allez dans Développeurs → Clés API dans votre tableau de bord B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:416
msgid "Copy the API key and store it safely."
msgstr "Copiez la clé API et conservez-la en lieu sûr."

#: includes/Admin.php:418
msgid "Step 2 — Configure the plugin"
msgstr "Étape 2 — Configurez le plugin"

#: includes/Admin.php:420
msgid "In WordPress, go to Invoices → Settings."
msgstr "Dans WordPress, allez dans Factures → Paramètres."

#: includes/Admin.php:421
msgid "Paste your B2Brouter API key."
msgstr "Collez votre clé API B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:422
msgid ""
"Click Validate Key. If the key is correct, the plugin will display your "
"account information."
msgstr ""
"Cliquez sur Valider la clé. Si la clé est correcte, le plugin affichera les "
"informations de votre compte."

#: includes/Admin.php:426
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Prérequis"

#: includes/Admin.php:428
msgid "A B2Brouter account with an active eDocExchange subscription"
msgstr "Un compte B2Brouter avec un abonnement eDocExchange actif"

#: includes/Admin.php:429
msgid "WordPress 5.8 or higher"
msgstr "WordPress 5.8 ou supérieur"

#: includes/Admin.php:430
msgid "WooCommerce 5.0 or higher, installed and active"
msgstr "WooCommerce 5.0 ou supérieur, installé et actif"

#: includes/Admin.php:431
msgid "PHP 7.4 or higher"
msgstr "PHP 7.4 ou supérieur"

#: includes/Admin.php:438
msgid "How it works"
msgstr "Comment ça fonctionne"

#: includes/Admin.php:440
msgid ""
"Advanced configuration (transports, formats, taxes) is done in your "
"B2Brouter account."
msgstr ""
"La configuration avancée (transports, formats, taxes) se fait dans votre "
"compte B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:441
msgid ""
"When an order is completed, the plugin automatically generates the invoice "
"via the B2Brouter API."
msgstr ""
"Lorsqu'une commande est terminée, le plugin génère automatiquement la "
"facture via l'API B2Brouter."

#: includes/Admin.php:442
msgid ""
"B2Brouter sends the invoice to your customer using your configured transport "
"(email, Peppol, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"B2Brouter envoie la facture à votre client en utilisant le transport "
"configuré (email, Peppol, etc.)."

#: includes/Admin.php:443
msgid ""
"Your customers can also download their invoices from their account page."
msgstr ""
"Vos clients peuvent également télécharger leurs factures depuis leur page de "
"compte."

#: includes/Admin.php:444
msgid "Credit notes are generated automatically when you process a refund."
msgstr ""
"Les avoirs sont générés automatiquement lorsque vous traitez un "
"remboursement."

#: includes/Admin.php:446
msgid "Ready to get started?"
msgstr "Prêt à commencer ?"

#: includes/Admin.php:449
msgid "Go to B2Brouter - Activate Subscription"
msgstr "Aller à B2Brouter - Activer l'abonnement"

