#: includes/Admin.php:460
msgid "Time Saving"
msgstr "Gain de temps"

#: includes/Admin.php:460
msgid ""
"Automatic generation of electronic invoices without manual intervention."
msgstr ""
"Génération automatique de factures électroniques sans intervention manuelle."

#: includes/Admin.php:461
