#: includes/Admin.php:858
msgid "Fallback Polling"
msgstr "Interrogation de secours"

#: includes/Admin.php:868
msgid ""
"Keep polling as backup (checks every 6 hours if webhook fails). Recommended "
"for reliability."
msgstr ""
"Conserver l'interrogation comme sauvegarde (vérifie toutes les 6 heures en "
"cas d'échec du webhook). Recommandé pour la fiabilité."

